oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: An Evening at the American Music Shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Parnell, Lee Roy; Brown, T. Graham; Berg, Matraca; Seals, Dan; Welch, Kevin; Skaggs, Ricky; McClinton, Delbert; O'Connor, Mark; Douglas, Jerry, 1956-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing An Evening at the American Music Shop featuring Lee Roy Parnell, T. Graham Brown, Matraca Berg, Dan Seals, Kevin Welch, Ricky Skaggs, Delbert McClinton, Mark O'Connor and the American Music Shop Band with Jerry Douglas, Harry Stinson, Brent Rowan, Matt Rollings, and Glenn Worf at the GEO Celebrity Theatre on October 13.
